Submit a Request for Loan Payoff Statement
The Request Loan Payoff Statement service process simplifies the way customers can manage and repay their loans.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled

Setup and Configuration of the Request Loan Payoff Statement Service Process
Use the Service Process Studio to enable the Request Loan Payoff Statement service process.
Your service agents can capture and submit a customer request for obtaining a loan payoff statement through the Request Loan Payoff Statement OmniScript. A case is then created in Salesforce.
